      • createRpcService

        public static RpcService createRpcService(java.lang.String hostname,
                                          int port,
                                          Configuration configuration)
                                   throws java.lang.Exception
        Utility method to create RPC service from configuration and hostname, port.
        参数:
        hostname - The hostname/address that describes the TaskManager's data location.
        port - If true, the TaskManager will not initiate the TCP network stack.
        configuration - The configuration for the TaskManager.
        返回:
        The rpc service which is used to start and connect to the TaskManager RpcEndpoint .
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - Thrown, if the actor system can not bind to the address
        java.lang.Exception - Thrown is some other error occurs while creating akka actor system

      • getRpcUrl

        public static java.lang.String getRpcUrl(java.lang.String hostname,
                                         int port,
                                         java.lang.String endpointName,
                                         HighAvailabilityServicesUtils.AddressResolution addressResolution,
                                         Configuration config)
                                  throws java.net.UnknownHostException
        参数:
        hostname - The hostname or address where the target RPC service is listening.
        port - The port where the target RPC service is listening.
        endpointName - The name of the RPC endpoint.
        addressResolution - Whether to try address resolution of the given hostname or not. This allows to fail fast in case that the hostname cannot be resolved.
        config - The configuration from which to deduce further settings.
        返回:
        The RPC URL of the specified RPC endpoint.
        抛出:
        java.net.UnknownHostException

      • getRpcUrl

        public static java.lang.String getRpcUrl(java.lang.String hostname,
                                         int port,
                                         java.lang.String endpointName,
                                         HighAvailabilityServicesUtils.AddressResolution addressResolution,
                                         AkkaRpcServiceUtils.AkkaProtocol akkaProtocol)
                                  throws java.net.UnknownHostException
        参数:
        hostname - The hostname or address where the target RPC service is listening.
        port - The port where the target RPC service is listening.
        endpointName - The name of the RPC endpoint.
        addressResolution - Whether to try address resolution of the given hostname or not. This allows to fail fast in case that the hostname cannot be resolved.
        akkaProtocol - True, if security/encryption is enabled, false otherwise.
        返回:
        The RPC URL of the specified RPC endpoint.
        抛出:
        java.net.UnknownHostException

      • createInetSocketAddressFromAkkaURL

        public static java.net.InetSocketAddress createInetSocketAddressFromAkkaURL(java.lang.String akkaURL)
                                                                     throws java.lang.Exception
        Extracts the hostname and the port of the remote actor system from the given Akka URL. The result is an InetSocketAddress instance containing the extracted hostname and port. If the Akka URL does not contain the hostname and port information, e.g. a local Akka URL is provided, then an Exception is thrown.
        参数:
        akkaURL - The URL to extract the host and port from.
        返回:
        The InetSocketAddress with teh extracted host and port.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - Thrown, if the given string does not represent a proper url
